Determine whether this social media post from Donald Trump is an insult to Kamala Harris. Simply return "yes" or "no".
content: I was the one who got the $35 Insulin, not Lyin’ Kamala. I’ve never seen a group that lies so much, like making up, out of thin air, that the U.S. produced 818,000 New Jobs, when it was a total fraud that they had to recant; or that she worked so hard at McDonalds, BUT SHE NEVER WORKED THERE. They even said that they knew nothing about Deranged Jack Smith going after their political opponent, ME - And that was the biggest lie of them all. But fear not, we will WIN and, MAKE AMERICA GREAT AGAIN!
